MATCH_TOOL: Bash
MATCH_PATTERN: (npm run dev|wrangler dev( |$)|scripts/tmp-create-game)
ADVISORY: |
  Worktree gotcha: `.dev.vars` is gitignored, so new worktrees never have it.
  Before starting dev servers or running scripts/tmp-create-game.* in a
  worktree, copy from the main repo:

    cp /Users/manu/Projects/pecking-order/apps/game-server/.dev.vars \
       apps/game-server/.dev.vars
    cp /Users/manu/Projects/pecking-order/apps/lobby/.dev.vars \
       apps/lobby/.dev.vars

  Without `AUTH_SECRET`, the worker rejects every magic-link WebSocket with
  close code 4001/4003, and useGameEngine.ts redirects the browser to
  `/?noRecover=1`. Symptom: magic link opens `/game/<code>?_t=...`, URL
  strips to `/game/<code>`, then instantly redirects to `/`. No visible
  error — console shows `[WS] Connection closed { code: 4001|4003 }`.

  Check first: `ls apps/game-server/.dev.vars apps/lobby/.dev.vars`.
  If either is missing, copy before proceeding.

  Real session cost: user reports this as recurring ("why does this keep
  happening"). See memory: feedback_worktree_devvars_setup.md.
